{"tid":2506502,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"政府研新App以顏色區分打針食客","createTime":"2021-04-27T10:57:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T11:21:38.000Z","uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"7a1788dc5927429cd37214c8e76b3704bf8c0475","tid":2506502,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:57:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210427/KULLVFLQXJHIBC2JPMMJFW34EM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210427%2FKULLVFLQXJHIBC2JPMMJFW34EM%2F&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oI429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=720c8802\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210427%2FKULLVFLQXJHIBC2JPMMJFW34EM%2F&h=b9e04e28\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210427/KULLVFLQXJHIBC2JPMMJFW34EM/</a><br />\n<br />\n研新App以顏色區分打針食客 讓食肆員工查客人資料<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;她又透露政府已研發一個新手機應用程式予食肆使用，食肆員工可用以掃描客人的二維碼以索取相關資料，並以顏色區分客人。<br />\n<br />\n劉利群補充，該應用程式分別以不同顏色區分已打一劑、已打兩劑並經過14天及資料錯誤的客人，以便員工快速識別。&hellip;"},{"pid":"9291ebbdd30c95f9cf2d3a7cc4cdd3ff7e8c3210","tid":2506502,"uid":89683,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:58:26.000Z","msg":"四色健康碼？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51d905c651d32824da60c9ac39e190ebb38438e6","tid":2506502,"uid":31296,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:58:28.000Z","msg":"社會信用制度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e71f3d2d6a8e83aaf9af1cb14c43bf11bec5e73e","tid":2506502,"uid":65888,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:58:35.000Z","msg":"黃vs藍isok"},{"pid":"ffc1343a69c3ab00da02e552edee0d365c811478","tid":2506502,"uid":146535,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"reply